cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a customized semantic segmentation task using multiview image streams. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper presents a semi-supervised learning framework for the segmentation task. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel network design that is agnostic to camera calibration, network model, and semantic category. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with 3D geometry and shape-from-silhouette. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper validates the proposed network on real-world visual data including social videos.
